Document summary: This document outlines the revised Community-Based Renewable Energy Program Phase 1, detailing the availability, customer participation, credit rates, developer participation, and other key aspects of the program. It establishes eligibility requirements, participation agreements, upfront payments, credit rates, and operational and maintenance fees for both participants and developers in the Phase 1 of the CBRE Program.
Suggested title v2: Community-Based Renewable Energy Program Phase 1 - Revised
